race.comment: The penny has dropped for GARINION RIGH (6) who has strung three wins together on the bounce with two of those victories coming over this track and trip. Winning hoop Sandkuhl sticks in the saddle and again gets the benefit of her 3kg claim. Rates the testing material. BETTER BREAKOUT (5) is another in a purple patch with back-to-back wins here and looks ready for the step-up to the mile journey now. Looms as the main danger. ULTIMATE (7) may have suffered from the dreaded second-up syndrome last time out but the form prior was full of merit. Worth another chance from the inside marble. CANDLELIT (3) doesn't win out of turn but is usually thereabouts and is a must for the multiples. RELEASE LE MISSILE (1) best of the rest.
